%TMPL:DEF{"bodystart"}%
<body class="twikiNoViewPage twikiAttachPage" onload="initForm()"><a name="PageTop"></a><div class="twikiPage">%TMPL:END%



%TMPL:DEF{"titleaction"}%(attach) %TMPL:END%



%TMPL:DEF{"simpleheader"}%
---+ Attach image or document on %TOPIC% %TMPL:END%



%TMPL:DEF{"notes"}%
   * *Help:* Please see %TWIKIWEB%.FileAttachment for more information about attaching files.
   * *Bug:* Internet Explorer 4.0 or earlier: If you get an "Internal Server Error" message when you upload a file, you need to try again. It should work the second time.
